snippet.title: Warhammer 40,000: Space Marine 2 - Official The Space Marine Arsenal Trailer
snippet.description:
Choose from a range of superheavy weapons to crush your enemies in Space Marine 2. Check out the latest Warhammer 40,000: Space Marine 2 trailer to see a variety of weapons and how you can switch between melee and ranged combats and adapt your strategy to obliterate your foes. 

Warhammer 40,000: Space Marine 2 will be available on PC, PS5, and Xbox Series X|S on September 9, 2024.
